      "text": "we pull a image, we run a contaner and we expec that, container will give us shell to work on but it \nwould not. because on last command bash command likhi hui hi ni h, Because last command is not bash\ncommand it will not give sheel to us. In that case we can inspect and check that shell is there or not.\nIn that case we can do using exec command and then we can run bash commmand.",
