      "updated": 1773934266412,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Docker's interview Question how will be asked?\n1 Architecture of Docker Container\n2 Architecture of Docker Container Vs VM\n3 basic commands of Docker\n    suppose we said docker stop\n    then they will ask what is diff between docker stop and docker kill\n    what is diff between save and commit\n    what is diff between commit and export\n    what is diff between export and import\n\nWe are done with Docker 70% except dockerfile, only dockerfile creation is pending",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Docker's interview Question how will be asked?\n1 Architecture of Docker Container\n2 Architecture of Docker Container Vs VM\n3 basic commands of Docker\n    suppose we said docker stop\n    then they will ask what is diff between docker stop and docker kill\n    what is diff between save and commit\n    what is diff between commit and export\n    what is diff between export and import\n\nWe are done with Docker 70% except dockerfile, only dockerfile creation is pending",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
