      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "task -> Dont use dockerfile, using ubuntu base image create a container and then setup \n        Apache web server inside it, but when we are setting up the Apache web server\n        make sure we note down each and every command that we are running.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "task -> Dont use dockerfile, using ubuntu base image create a container and then setup \n        Apache web server inside it, but when we are setting up the Apache web server\n        make sure we note down each and every command that we are running.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
